title: Toni Braxton - Toni Braxton (2 CD Deluxe Edition) (2016)
description:
2 CD Deluxe Edition with 21 Bonus Tracks. Throughout her career, Toni has sold over 67 million records, including 41 million albums, worldwide. She has won seven Grammy Awards, nine Billboard Music Awards, seven American Music Awards and several other awards. Aside from her success in music, Braxton has become a television executive producer and personality, being involved in the 7th season of the reality show Dancing with the Stars and in a reality series entitled Braxton Family Values.
